channel.title: My runserver has a life of its own! help!
channel.description: ok, so i got done with some editing and i click compile and after that i start runserver but it says "Unable to startup listener on port 43594 -- port already in use?" and so i was sondering what was going on because there wasn't another runserver going so i log into 0.0.0.0 and realize my server is running, but my runserver isn't, anyone know what happened?
